    <entry>
      <title>CentOS9服务器搭建01-远程连接被拒绝问题解决</title>
      <link href="/2024/03/28/centos9-fu-wu-qi-da-jian-01/"/>
      <url>/2024/03/28/centos9-fu-wu-qi-da-jian-01/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<blockquote><p>CentOS Stream 9 的 Linux内核版本是 5.14.0，已经算是非常新版本了。<br>这里关于系统的安装问题，我们就跳过了，网上大把的教程，大家可以自行搜搜<br>CentOS Stream 9 安装完成，离真正可用的服务器还缺点东西<br>网络和软件，本文就是连接网络过程中遇到的一些问题总结</p></blockquote><h2 id="环境"><a href="#环境" class="headerlink" title="环境"></a>环境</h2><blockquote><p>VMware 17.5.1<br><br>CentOS Stream 9</p></blockquote><ul><li><p>获取<a href="https://www.centos.org/centos-stream/">安装包</a>进行安装</p></li><li><p>查看系统版本号</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># 查看 CentOS 版本号</span><br><span class="line">cat /etc/redhat-release</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"># 查看 Linux 内核版本号</span><br><span class="line">uname -r</span><br><span class="line">或 </span><br><span class="line">uname -a</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure></li><li><p>查看防火墙状态</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">systemctl status firewalld</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure></li><li><p>查看已开放的端口列表</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">firewall-cmd --list-port</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure></li><li><p>开启 <code>80</code> 端口权限并让端口生效</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta prompt_"># </span><span class="language-bash">开启端口</span></span><br><span class="line">firewall-cmd --zone=public --add-port=80/tcp --permanent</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta prompt_"># </span><span class="language-bash">重载防火墙，让端口权限生效</span></span><br><span class="line">firewall-cmd --reload</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure></li><li><p>ssh用户密码正确但是登录时却报被拒绝</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># 打开配置文件</span><br><span class="line">cd /etc/ssh/</span><br><span class="line">vi sshd_config</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"># 在文件中添加如下配置</span><br><span class="line">PermitRootLogin yes</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"># 重启 ssh 服务</span><br><span class="line">systemctl restart sshd</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"># 注意：这里可能会报错，我因为写错了命令，报错如下：</span><br><span class="line">Job for sshd.service failed because the control process exited with error code.</span><br><span class="line">See "systemctl status sshd.service" and "journalctl -xeu sshd.service" for details.</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"># 如果找不到问题所在，可以在当前目录下执行以下命令，会显示出来具体错误位置</span><br><span class="line">sshd -T</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">按如上操作后，再次连接即可完成登录成功</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure></li></ul>]]></content>
      
      
      <categories>
          
          <category> CentOS9服务器搭建 </category>
          
      </categories>
      
      
